 EDITOR HELPTo enter the editor command mode, type [ESC] Z.In the editor command mode, type E to enter the editor.In the editor, type [CTRL] Q for a menu of edit commands.To exit the editor and return to the editor command mode, type [ESC].To exit the editor command mode, type Q (for Quit) and Y (for Yes).   TERMINAL --[ESC] Z-->  EDITOR   ---E-->                         COMMAND             EDITOR     MODE    <--QY---      MODE  <--[ESC]--